column5: Finally got out fishing for lakers.  Ice just went out last week.  Too windy for trolling so we just fished of the bank with ciscoes.  Went out with my son, brother in law, and two nephews.  Caught three in about 3 1/2 hours of fishing.  A little slow but we still enjoyed ourselves.
Great stuff Rickster...thanks for sharing. Great to get the young lads out with you.
WTG!!   Nice day fishing and another entry for team 9..WOOHOO  Bly
